if you wants to use php then you need an virtual machine to run the php code or script. So here is the solution for your laptop or computer:

> you can download XAMPP and install as your OS standard!
> Choose a folder - where you install the softwere.
> install properly as required! [important]
> In php we can easily use HTML without any issues
> If the .php extention after the index not written then the php wont work!
> If Apache server in turn on then the php will work perfectly
> If you wants to use MySql database then turn on the MySql Server in Xammp
